# 把一个简单的div元素的属性都打印出来

```
var docu = document.createElement('div')
var str = '';
for(var key in docu){
	str += key+'';
}
"_NODEATTRIBUTE_NODETEXT_NODECDATA_SECTION_NODEENTITY_REFERENCE_NODEENTITY_NODEPROCESSING_INSTRUCTION_NODECOMMENT_NODEDOCUMENT_NODEDOCUMENT_TYPE_NODEDOCUMENT_FRAGMENT_NODENOTATION_NODEDOCUMENT_POSITION_DISCONNECTEDDOCUMENT_POSITION_PRECEDINGDOCUMENT_POSITION_FOLLOWINGDOCUMENT_POSITION_CONTAINSDOCUMENT_POSITION_CONTAINED_BYDOCUMENT_POSITION_IMPLEMENTATION_"
```
